to the ER, right?

51:00.474 --> 51:03.310
Tomorrow, Frank.
Today, dance with me.

51:03.394 --> 51:06.021
Hold me.
Tell me I'm okay.

51:06.105 --> 51:09.233
You're okay.

51:09.316 --> 51:11.277
<i>♪♪♪</i>

51:11.360 --> 51:12.861
Everything‐‐everything
is gonna be okay.

51:12.945 --> 51:16.865
[Lip]
Excuse me, excuse me.

51:16.949 --> 51:18.993
A fuckin' house party, Frank?
What grade are you in?

51:19.076 --> 51:22.204
Grade A!
Frank's the best grade.

51:24.206 --> 51:26.083
Jesus Christ.

51:26.166 --> 51:30.671
<i>♪♪♪</i>

51:30.754 --> 51:33.841
[Kevin]
And finally, number 14.

51:36.218 --> 51:40.055
