‐ Mm.

51:44.727 --> 51:47.271
I could listen to you
for hours, Kevin.

51:47.354 --> 51:48.230
[Kevin chuckles]

51:48.314 --> 51:52.026
Thank you, number 14.
You may be seated.

51:52.109 --> 51:54.445
And that concludes
our interview portion.

51:54.528 --> 51:56.697
It's tough to stay
at this time, but right now,

51:56.780 --> 51:59.158
I think, uh, number 14
might be in the lead.

51:59.241 --> 52:00.743
Are you serious?

52:00.826 --> 52:03.746
