52:03.829 --> 52:06.832
I ask, you answer‐‐
just simple word association.

52:06.915 --> 52:08.834
Can we get
another round of shots?

52:08.917 --> 52:11.962
Yes.
Gretzky or Orr?

52:12.046 --> 52:14.173
