‐ [all] Gretzky.

52:14.256 --> 52:17.092
Gretzky.
Hoops or soccer?

52:17.176 --> 52:19.178
‐ [all] Hoops.
‐ Excellent.

52:19.261 --> 52:21.639
Polo shirt or tank top
with gold chains?

52:21.722 --> 52:22.181
‐ Polo shirt.
‐ [all] Tank‐‐

52:22.264 --> 52:24.892
Who said polo shirt?

52:24.975 --> 52:26.685
You're gone, 7.

52:26.769 --> 52:28.729
Auf wiedersehen.

52:28.812 --> 52:30.648
Mm‐hmm.
Finally.

52:32.191 --> 52:33.067
Fries and a Frosty at Wendy's

52:33.150 --> 52:37.196
or off the menu MexiMelt
at Taco Bell?

52:37.279 --> 52:38.530
‐ [all] MexiMelt.
‐ MexiMelt.

52:38.614 --> 52:39.448
‐ MexiMelt.
‐ [door slams]

52:39.531 --> 52:42.034
Oh, hey, V.
There she is, everyone!

52:42.117 --> 52:43.577
‐ Say hi, V.
‐ [all] Hi, V.

52:43.661 --> 52:47.539
Hi, ladies...

52:47.623 --> 52:49.750
Who are they?

52:49.833 --> 52:51.669
Oh, they're his Tinder dates.

52:51.752 --> 52:54.129
But he's doing it
out of love for you.

52:54.213 --> 52:54.963
Yeah.

52:55.047 --> 52:56.298
His what?

52:56.382 --> 52:59.259
<i>♪ muffled rock music ♪</i>

52:59.343 --> 53:01.095
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:01.178 --> 53:02.388
Thanks for coming to the game
with me, little man.

53:02.471 --> 53:04.056
Thanks for taking me, MaVar.

53:04.139 --> 53:05.557
‐ [retching]
‐ Uh...

53:05.641 --> 53:07.601
You know, you sure
we shouldn't take you back

53:07.685 --> 53:08.936
to the bar we dropped
Veronica off at?

53:09.019 --> 53:11.563
This is my home.
Gotta face my fate.

53:11.647 --> 53:13.691
All right.
Let's do it again, okay?

53:13.774 --> 53:15.025
Definitely.

53:15.109 --> 53:17.069
‐ Have a good night.
‐ All right.

53:17.152 --> 53:19.029
[man] I'm gonna cut you,
motherfucker!

53:19.113 --> 53:20.864
[indistinct shouting
and laughter]

53:20.948 --> 53:23.617
[all] Fight, fight, fight!

53:23.701 --> 53:25.035
‐ Fight, fight, fight...
‐ Sorry.

53:25.119 --> 53:26.328
Look, I can't leave you here.

53:26.412 --> 53:27.663
You know how to play
Nintendo Wii?

53:27.746 --> 53:29.456
‐ Yeah.
‐ All right, let's go.

53:29.540 --> 53:32.292
Maybe grill some steaks,
watch <i>Do the Right Thing.</i>

53:32.376 --> 53:34.503
‐ You know who Spike Lee is?
‐ Yep.

53:34.586 --> 53:36.588
All right, of course you do.

53:36.672 --> 53:41.427
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:42.177 --> 53:42.761
Sorry about him.
Get home safely.

53:42.845 --> 53:44.805
Godspeed.

53:44.888 --> 53:46.098
[Kevin]
Thanks for playing.

53:46.181 --> 53:48.058
Sorry about him.
Have a good night.

53:48.142 --> 53:49.727
Go with God.
Thanks for playing.

53:49.810 --> 53:52.563
‐ Sorry.
‐ You can keep that.

53:52.646 --> 53:56.567
You know, there's an app for
making platonic friends, dick.

53:56.650 --> 53:57.776
‐ FriendFinder.
‐ Good to know.

53:57.860 --> 54:01.071
Thanks for playing.

54:01.155 --> 54:02.406
That everyone?

54:04.366 --> 54:06.243
I'll get her some coffee.

54:06.910 --> 54:09.329
‐ Hey.
‐ Hey, man.

54:09.413 --> 54:11.623
Thanks for letting me crash
tonight, seriously.

54:11.707 --> 54:12.916
Yeah.
Hey...

54:13.000 --> 54:14.501
Are you sure you don't
want to stay at the house?

54:14.585 --> 54:15.252
‐ Crash on the couch?
‐ Nah.

54:15.335 --> 54:17.254
The whole block's loud as shit

54:17.337 --> 54:18.547
and I don't want
to put you guys out.

54:18.630 --> 54:19.047
It's all good.
This is‐‐this is good.

54:19.131 --> 54:20.799
All right, man.

54:20.883 --> 54:21.967
Seat yourself.

54:22.050 --> 54:24.219
Take any booth you like.

54:24.303 --> 54:26.388
Frank usually sleeps
in that one.

54:26.472 --> 54:28.098
[sighing]
Okay.

54:28.182 --> 54:31.018
<i>♪ laidback guitar music ♪</i>

54:31.101 --> 54:35.397
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:35.481 --> 54:38.192
[door rattling]

54:42.362 --> 54:43.447
Got my shit?

54:43.530 --> 54:45.032
You got mine?

54:45.115 --> 54:48.410
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:58.420 --> 55:01.256
FaceTime your brother.
See the baby.

55:03.383 --> 55:06.929
You got five minutes,
starting now.

55:10.724 --> 55:12.643
[door sliding shut]

55:12.726 --> 55:14.645
[Veronica]
Rise and shine.

55:16.939 --> 55:18.440
Did I win?

55:18.524 --> 55:20.776
There's nothing to win.
There never was.

55:20.859 --> 55:23.904
My husband's a bit disturbed.
Sorry.

55:25.155 --> 55:28.033
I got you some coffee though.

55:28.116 --> 55:30.160
Oh, my God, thank you.

55:30.244 --> 55:31.703
Hope you didn't ruin
your whole night.

55:31.787 --> 55:32.162
‐ [laughter]
‐ Nah.

55:32.246 --> 55:33.580
It was fun.

55:33.664 --> 55:37.376
Free drinks and my kid's
with my ex all weekend...

55:37.459 --> 55:40.212
Girl's gotta put on lashes and
lipstick every one in a while.

55:40.295 --> 55:42.839
Yeah, gotta remember
you're not dead,

55:42.923 --> 55:44.383
even though you
basically are as a mom.

55:44.466 --> 55:46.051
[chuckles]

55:46.134 --> 55:48.387
Got twin girls.
How old's your kid?

55:48.470 --> 55:50.138
Six.
Jared.

55:50.222 --> 55:52.558
Like the jewelry store.

55:52.641 --> 55:55.227
Right.
"He went to Jared."

55:55.310 --> 55:57.354
Too bad no one's ever
going to Jared for me.

55:57.437 --> 55:59.189
I had to buy this for myself.

55:59.273 --> 56:00.857
A little self‐care.

56:00.941 --> 56:02.818
I put jewels and decals
and shit on my nails.

56:02.901 --> 56:05.362
My little treat.

56:05.445 --> 56:07.489
It's hard to get out
when you're our age.

56:07.573 --> 56:08.740
So hard.

56:08.824 --> 56:09.616
Hard to meet people.

56:09.700 --> 56:13.161
It's hard to put yourself
out there.

56:13.245 --> 56:15.080
I'm Mimi.

56:15.163 --> 56:15.831
Well, Mei Ling, but Mimi.

56:15.914 --> 56:20.794
Veronica, but V.

56:20.877 --> 56:22.421
[Mimi]
Do you wanna get a nightcap, V?

56:22.504 --> 56:24.923
Maybe somewhere that
people aren't staring?

56:25.007 --> 56:27.634
[Veronica]
Yeah.

56:30.262 --> 56:33.599
<i>♪ bluesy rock music ♪</i>

56:33.682 --> 56:34.975
Bye, best friends.
Have fun.

56:35.058 --> 56:39.021
<i>♪♪♪</i>

56:39.104 --> 56:42.107
[phone ringing]

56:42.190 --> 56:47.154
<i>♪♪♪</i>

56:52.784 --> 56:54.119
