‐ Ian?

56:54.202 --> 56:56.622
How the hell are you
on FaceTime?

56:56.705 --> 56:58.123
<i>Can I see the baby?</i>

56:58.206 --> 57:00.042
Yeah, yeah, no, he's, uh,

57:00.125 --> 57:03.629
he's right here.

57:03.712 --> 57:05.339
<i>♪♪♪</i>

57:05.422 --> 57:09.384
Hey, buddy, whoa.

57:09.468 --> 57:11.970
[Lip]
Eight pounds, eight ounces.

57:12.054 --> 57:14.890
This is Fred.

57:14.973 --> 57:18.310
Fred, hey, hey!
