57:18.393 --> 57:20.103
Hello.

57:20.187 --> 57:21.813
Lip, you have a son.

57:21.897 --> 57:24.149
Yeah, I do.

57:24.232 --> 57:27.819
Yeah, fuck.
[laughs]

57:27.903 --> 57:29.237
<i>Hey, buddy.</i>

57:29.321 --> 57:31.615
<i>♪♪♪</i>

57:31.698 --> 57:33.367
Fred Gallagher, huh?

57:33.450 --> 57:35.661
